# Force LF line endings on shell scripts so they execute correctly in
# Linux containers (Railway, Docker). Without this, files authored on
# Windows would get CRLF and Linux would error: `bad interpreter: No such
# file or directory` or silent exit on the first line.
*.sh text eol=lf
Dockerfile text eol=lf
*.dockerignore text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
